</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="9098651CB876EB099E50FA1CE3A1C5FE" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" type="description">
<paragraph id="D83D3697B876EB099E50FA1CE3A1C5FE" blockId="13.[111,648,1484,1700]" lastBlockId="13.[675,1212,216,908]" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">
<bibRefCitation id="BC134B66B876EB099E50FA1CE63EC070" author="TOULGOET H. &amp; DE" box="[113,293,1515,1541]" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" pagination="127 - 136" refId="ref20600" refString="TOULGOET H. DE 1991. - Le genre Trichromia Hubner 1816. Caracteristiques, composition et limites. (Lepidoptera Arctiidae Arctiinae) (37 e note). Lambillionea 91 (2): 127 - 136." type="journal article" year="1991">Toulgoët (1991)</bibRefCitation>
, lors de sa révision du genre 
<taxonomicName id="1F824D14B876EB099C7CFA1CE7DEC051" authorityName="Hubner" authorityYear="1819" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Trichromia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="EAF6EA85B876EB099C7CFA1CE7DEC051" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">Trichromia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
met en synonymie les genres 
<taxonomicName id="1F824D14B876EB099C33F9FCE564C051" authorityName="Hampson" authorityYear="1901" box="[530,639,1547,1572]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Paranerita" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="EAF6EA85B876EB099C33F9FCE564C051" box="[530,639,1547,1572]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">Paranerita</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="1F824D14B876EB099E50F9DCE662C031" authority="Hampson, 1901" authorityName="Hampson" authorityYear="1901" box="[113,377,1578,1605]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Parevia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="EAF6EA85B876EB099E50F9DCE7A5C031" box="[113,190,1579,1604]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">Parevia</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="BC134B66B876EB099EE7F9DCE662C031" author="HAMPSON G. F." box="[198,377,1578,1605]" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" refId="ref19615" refString="HAMPSON G. F. 1901. - Catalogue of the Lepidoptera Phalaenae in the British Museum 3. Printed by order of the Trustees, London: 690 p." type="book" year="1901">Hampson, 1901</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
et 
<taxonomicName id="1F824D14B876EB099FBDF9DCE599C030" authority="Walker, 1855" authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1855" box="[412,642,1578,1605]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Neritos" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="EAF6EA85B876EB099FBDF9DCE6FDC031" box="[412,486,1579,1604]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">Neritos</emphasis>
Walker, 1855
</taxonomicName>
. Cependant, au sein de sa liste récapitulative du genre 
<emphasis id="EAF6EA85B876EB099E4EF99EE7F0C0F6" box="[111,235,1641,1667]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">
<taxonomicName id="1F824D14B876EB099E4EF99EE7FDC0F6" authorityName="Hubner" authorityYear="1819" box="[111,230,1641,1667]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Trichromia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Trichromia</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
il omet plusieurs espèces alors incluses au sein du genre 
<taxonomicName id="1F824D14B876EB099F13F97DE666C0D6" authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1855" box="[306,381,1674,1699]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Neritos" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="EAF6EA85B876EB099F13F97DE666C0D6" box="[306,381,1674,1699]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">Neritos</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Bien qu’absentes de la liste récapitulative de 
<bibRefCitation id="BC134B66B876EB099DB0FF2FE35CC687" author="TOULGOET H. &amp; DE" box="[913,1095,216,242]" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" pagination="127 - 136" refId="ref20600" refString="TOULGOET H. DE 1991. - Le genre Trichromia Hubner 1816. Caracteristiques, composition et limites. (Lepidoptera Arctiidae Arctiinae) (37 e note). Lambillionea 91 (2): 127 - 136." type="journal article" year="1991">Toulgoët (1991)</bibRefCitation>
, et n’étant pas explicitement exclues du genre 
<taxonomicName id="1F824D14B876EB099A3DFF00E38BC764" authorityName="Hubner" authorityYear="1819" box="[1052,1168,247,273]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Trichromia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="EAF6EA85B876EB099A3DFF00E38BC764" box="[1052,1168,247,273]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">Trichromia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
par l’auteur de cette révision, ces espèces appartiennent donc bien au genre 
<taxonomicName id="1F824D14B876EB099D5CFEC0E4EAC724" authorityName="Hubner" authorityYear="1819" box="[893,1009,311,337]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Trichromia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="EAF6EA85B876EB099D5CFEC0E4EAC724" box="[893,1009,311,337]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">Trichromia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
du fait de la mise en synonymie du genre 
<taxonomicName id="1F824D14B876EB099D97FEA0E319C705" authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1855" box="[950,1026,343,368]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Neritos" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="EAF6EA85B876EB099D97FEA0E319C705" box="[950,1026,343,368]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">Neritos</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Parmi celles-ci, l’espèce 
<taxonomicName id="1F824D14B876EB099CDCFE80E35EC7E4" authority="Sepp, 1855" authorityName="Sepp" authorityYear="1855" box="[765,1093,374,401]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Neritos" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="leucostigma">
<emphasis id="EAF6EA85B876EB099CDCFE80E4DFC7E5" box="[765,964,374,400]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">Neritos leucostigma</emphasis>
Sepp, 1855
</taxonomicName>
est décrite du 
<collectingCountry id="A0957607B876EB099CEDFE61E434C7C5" box="[716,815,406,432]" name="Suriname" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">Surinam</collectingCountry>
, à partir d’un nombre inconnu de 
<typeStatus id="07398835B876EB099C86FE41E41DC7A5" box="[679,774,438,464]" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">syntypes</typeStatus>
. Aucun des 
<typeStatus id="07398835B876EB099DABFE41E4FEC7A5" box="[906,997,438,464]" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">syntypes</typeStatus>
de Sepp n’ayant pu être localisé, seules les figures de sa planche en vue dorsale et ventrale, permettent de discriminer ce taxon. Les ornementations des ailes antérieures sont différentes de celles des représentants de son genre. Elles montrent une tache réniforme claire et de multiples taches arrondies orangées. Les ailes postérieures sont très arrondies. Cet habitus correspond en réalité au genre 
<taxonomicName id="1F824D14B876EB099DF5FD44E3AEC4BB" authority="Walker, 1854" authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1854" box="[980,1205,691,718]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Melese" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="EAF6EA85B876EB099DF5FD44E30CC4B8" box="[980,1047,691,717]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">Melese</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="BC134B66B876EB099A01FD44E3AEC4BB" author="WALKER F." box="[1056,1205,691,718]" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" pagination="279 - 581" refId="ref21006" refString="WALKER F. 1854. - List of the Specimens of Lepidopterous Insects in the Collection of the British Museum 2: 279 - 581. London." type="journal article" year="1854">Walker, 1854</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, et plus particulièrement à l’espèce 
<taxonomicName id="1F824D14B876EB099A0AFD24E445C578" authority="Rothschild, 1909" authorityName="Rothschild" authorityYear="1909" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Melese" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="drucei">
<emphasis id="EAF6EA85B876EB099A0AFD24E3A1C498" box="[1067,1210,723,749]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">Melese drucei</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="BC134B66B876EB099C84FD05E445C578" author="ROTHSCHILD L. W." box="[677,862,754,781]" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" pagination="21 - 299" refId="ref20254" refString="ROTHSCHILD L. W. 1909. - Descriptions of some new South American Arctiadae, with notes. Novitates Zoologicae 16: 21 - 299." type="journal article" year="1909">Rothschild, 1909</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
décrite du 
<collectingCountry id="A0957607B876EB099DF2FD05E328C579" box="[979,1075,754,780]" name="Suriname" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">Surinam</collectingCountry>
. Cependant, n’ayant pu localiser et étudier le 
<typeStatus id="07398835B876EB099A26FCE4E342C558" box="[1031,1113,787,813]" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">syntype</typeStatus>
de Sepp afin de confirmer cette hypothèse de synonymie, nous proposons uniquement la recombinaison au sein du genre 
<taxonomicName id="1F824D14B876EB099D19FC86E460C5FE" authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1854" box="[824,891,881,907]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Melese" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="EAF6EA85B876EB099D19FC86E460C5FE" box="[824,891,881,907]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="438">Melese</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
et non la mise en synonymie.
</paragraph>
